  "text": "You spoke of an Iranian Confederation and a battle being fought between the Confederation and the Iranian Confederation. Is it possible to convey any concept of how this battle was fought? I am Ra picture, if you will, your mind. Picture it then in total unity with all other minds of your society. You are then single-minded and that which is a weak electrical charge in your physical illusion is now an enormously powerful machine whereby thoughts may be projected as things. The result a stand off, as you would call it, both energies being somewhat depleted by this and needing to regroup. The negative depleted through failure to manipulate, the positive depleted through failure to accept that which is given.",
